  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will benefit 500 farmers organized in two cooperatives directly and their families indirectly by: 

(1) Improving the organizational, administrative and financial capacities of two cocoa cooperatives in order to increase access to certification and financial services; and 
(2) Improving the quality of cocoa produced and processed as well as value added through organic certification and the branding of artisanal chocolates for increased market access for sustainably produced cocoa.</narrative>
